@startuml
title Vue de déploiement — CanTelcoX

node "Docker - Réseau cantelcox-network" {

  node "Entrée & observabilité" {
    component "KrakenD\nAPI Gateway\n:8080" as Gateway
    component "Prometheus\n:9090" as Prometheus
    component "Grafana\n:3000" as Grafana
    component "Locust\n:8089" as Locust
  }

  node "Services applicatifs" {
    component "Customer Identity Service\ncustomer_identity_api.py\n:5001\n/health" as CustomerService
    component "Commerce Service\ncommerce_api.py\n:5002\n/health" as CommerceService
  }

  node "Données" {
    database "MySQL Identity\nidentity_db\nvolume: mysql_identity_data" as MySQL1
    database "MySQL Commerce\ncommerce_db\nvolume: mysql_commerce_data" as MySQL2
    database "Redis\n:6379" as Redis
  }
}

Gateway --> CustomerService : /v1/customers/*\n/v1/auth/*
Gateway --> CommerceService : /v1/catalog/*\n/v1/orders/*\n/v1/lines/*\n/v1/usage/*\n/v1/invoices/*

CustomerService --> MySQL1 : SQL
CommerceService --> MySQL2 : SQL
CommerceService --> Redis : cache catalogue / usage / factures

Prometheus --> CustomerService : scrape /metrics
Prometheus --> CommerceService : scrape /metrics
Grafana --> Prometheus : datasource
Locust --> Gateway : tests de charge

@enduml